 supportiveness on the one hand and aggression, deception and self interest on the other. A set of coherent support and control polices for family relations are developed which endorse this awareness and embrace a fundamental shift in perspective for future progressive governments.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aFamily policyzGreat Britain. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / Marriage & Family.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-1995z978311119621340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447300540423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447300540/original  a978-3-11-119621-3  Bristol University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-1995c1995d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK